title: PrepXtra: Webb wins third consecutive state volleyball title
text:
PrepXtra: Webb wins third consecutive state volleyball title Spartans dominate Harding Academy Post to Facebook PrepXtra: Webb wins third consecutive state volleyball title Spartans dominate Harding Academy  //on.wbir.com/1LSvrVS   Join the Conversation To   PrepXtra: Webb wins third consecutive state volleyball title Tom Wood, PrepXtra 3:09 p.m. EDT October 23, 2015 Webb volleyball won its third-straight state championship (Photo: PrepXtra/WBIR) CONNECT 1 TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
MURFREESBORO â€” The three-peat is complete. 
And don't expect the state streak to end anytime soon, Webb School players said after the Spartans (53-4) wrapped up their third consecutive Division II-A volleyball championship with a dominating 3-0 victory over Harding Academy, 25-17, 25-14, 25-21, on Friday at the Murphy Center on the campus of Middle Tennessee State University.
